{"tid":1913451,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"（絲入）好奇女人有幾多唇膏、唇軸","createTime":"2020-03-06T19:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T16:26:31.000Z","uid":202377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"fe718ae42a6e75189f1a00e1d8db9eba3eee404e","tid":1913451,"uid":202377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T19:51:54.000Z","msg":"有色潤唇膏都計，總之有色就計"},{"pid":"0e5a7ed767189e07aa7a46e3c1d55b2215eea989","tid":1913451,"uid":228518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:27:09.000Z","msg":"我唔化妝 但會搽唇膏 我有3枝 但一枝比男朋友整斷咗 一枝唔好用 剩返個一枝就係常用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3b3ab8245d391f3b1571ec1d4fcb20ebec887f","tid":1913451,"uid":71085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:40:22.000Z","msg":"8枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後尾發現上嘴都係撚樣就無再買"},{"pid":"ba8b38982c2621f99d919c4ec885aac7cedcd31f","tid":1913451,"uid":200604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:42:25.000Z","msg":"我啲fd真係有成最少三十幾枝 even同色都要試唔同牌子<br />\n加上近排興韓式漸變 塗個咀都要用兩支 <br />\n<br />\n我自己就一支潤唇膏，一支咀嘅sleeping mask，三枝紅色(淺、深，同埋唇膏同唇軸都有)，一枝打底<br />\n<br />\n潤唇膏半年用哂一支，真係用到盡先扔<br />\n紅色個啲用極都用唔完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我無意慾想買唇膏"},{"pid":"7924b3c1b2706f6f55f46cc85b82b7e6a169a754","tid":1913451,"uid":140792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:52:55.000Z","msg":"我自己有40幾支<br />\n身邊大部分朋友都差唔多<br />\n其實女人儲唇膏就同男人鐘意儲鞋儲錶個原理一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明知用唔完都買 鬼叫自己鐘意咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f976a1e72aa9b691f7e1d938d9b8c87952dd872c","tid":1913451,"uid":310342,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-